\insrsid11761595\charrsid3743759 L}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 iberal, because of course in those days it was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11477449\charrsid3743759 L}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
