La}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 bour }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11477449\charrsid3743759 P}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 arty to support.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 And can you remember what makes you, what you know that makes you know that he was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11477449\charrsid3743759 L}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 iberal? Did he talk much about his views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Well we heard us children, thi
s is again when we were growing up a bit, but we heard as children his opinions of the candidate, of the local candidate, but I would think as far as parliamentary was concerned he wouldn't be concerned at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 No. Only local politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Only local
 politics. And then of course he had great admiration for quite a few of the business people and especially as we lived in East ward. He liked the people who were standing in East ward because they were usually East business people.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. Why do you think he had this admiration for business people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Possibly because he was so close to his own boss. He was a nice man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. He had a good relationship?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Very good, yes. Yes. He was a foreman and thought a good bit of in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. Your father was a foreman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 
And when you say he wasn't much interested in national politics, do you remember if he ever voted before 1918? In the elections of 1906, or don't you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 I don't. I didn't know any difference then between local and parliamentary.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 No. But do you remember him voting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Oh yes, I remember. I was taken to the voting stations with him. Yes I know that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. And you think that he always supported the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11477449\charrsid3743759 L}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 iberal candidates?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 I would say yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. Would he talk quite openly about where his allegiance lay in politics?
