No. I remember someone coming to the door when I was in my teens and being told that this is my opinion that I keep to myself - one's political ideals should }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12919142\charrsid3743759 not be}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759  divulged to other people.
