\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes, yes. But it was, but I mean you did get in and out of the houses of your friends?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 It was very free?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Oh yes. Very free. We were all very friendly, very nice people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 And was your own home the same in this way? Or it would wear off wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. I was allowed to have a friend or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12919142\charrsid3743759 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759  into the garden but we had such a sparse garden, such a poor sort of arrangement for children to play in that they weren't very keen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 And these children of these families, you met them at school did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 What about before you went to school? Do you remember who you played with then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Before I went to school I don't suppose I went out of the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 How old were you when you started school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12919142\charrsid3743759 5}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 And did you play much with your elder brother and sister, or was the gap too large?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 
They were far too old to play with me. Except, I suppose, in little games indoors, if I wanted amusing. Of course there was such a wide gap you see, nearly }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12919142\charrsid3743759 8}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759  years between my brother and I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. And did you feel closer to your brother or your sister or did you feel much the same about both of them during this period?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 I think of the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12919142\charrsid3743759 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759  I loved my brother very much. I always thought that I woul
d want to marry somebody like him when I grew up. I always said I wanted somebody like my brother, but I'm glad I didn't have anybody like him now though. We were too much of a muchness. My sister was very good to me, but again you see, she was a grown yo
ung woman and quite remote.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. On the question of who you played with, had your mother or father any occasion to discourage you from playing with certain children?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes from the area that my father was adverse to. In Northern Road area there were one or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12919142\charrsid3743759 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759  perhaps questionable families, not very clean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 And I made an acquaintance with one or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12919142\charrsid3743759 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759  of them from school but I was soon discouraged from joining them because they weren't desirable sort of children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 What were his things that he objected to then? You mentioned cleanliness, what sort of... 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 
Well, yes. Cleanliness and again I suppose it was a little bit of snobbishness here, that their mother and father were not quite the right type that he would like us to associate with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 It sounds a little bit arrogant I know but as a child one doesn't see that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 You see somebody that you like but you don't see behind that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 But both my parents did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. At that time do you remember your parents or other people making any distinction between rough and respectable people using the words.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes, again I think this comes into it that these people were of the very rough type.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 And the father I remember, the father of one of the girls was a drunkard and I think perhaps this swayed my people a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. Did you, were you upset by this prohibition on this particular child or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 No I think I was such a happy sort of kid that I got over it very quickly and went back to my original friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 You had plenty didn't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. Oh yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12919142\charrsid3743759 There's a question - did you go to a youth organisation at all? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 
You told me about the Welfare Club, was that the only thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes, that was the only thing that I was really interested in. Again, this would be from when I was about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9726110\charrsid3743759 11 }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 years old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. And hobbies? The rabbits that were kept, were they an interest of yours or more your elder brother and sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Oh, I think that until during the wartime they were my brother's interest more but of course naturally I had to put my nose into it as well.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 When you said you had to you mean you were inquisitive to, or it was necessary?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Oh yes, there was always an interest. I wanted to make quite sure the rabbi
t would run down my blouse the same as it would down my brother's shirt.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 When you were a child you had some hobbies and collected things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 On dolls and dolls' furniture.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. You collected it did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. And what my sister had finished with the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11761595\charrsid3743759 m }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 I was allowed to have}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11761595\charrsid3743759  them}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 
, and we were always taught to keep them in excellent condition. Not like the children of today that can throw them away the next minute. I've got things now in my cupboard that belonged to my sister and then they were handed to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. That is, you mean toys or clothes as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 
Oh toys, of course we had to share our clothes. Yes. But of toys, dolls, I had many. I think I can remember at least twelve dolls sitting along the settee occasionally when they all had to be put to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 You used to spend quite a long time on them doing things for them did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 What about any other sorts of things, you know, did you have any other sort of collections? Stamps or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 No. No there was nothing. I can only remember my dolls and my dolls}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11761595\charrsid3743759 \rquote }
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 
furniture. We had a room that was a spare bedroom when my sister moved out of it, it was used as a play room. Well before my sister moved into it, it was used as a play room. It was given back t
o me as a more or less store room for all my stuff. About the only thing I can remember was that I loved my dolls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. Quite a lot you had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes, of different kinds.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. Did you sew for them? Make clothes for them or anything like that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Well no, I didn't like sewing, but I might cut something out and put it on, you know, and just stitch it up. But it wasn't very well done.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 What about other sorts of handiwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 At the Welfare Club we used to do raffia work which I liked very much indeed. With the string and raffia.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes, we used to do quite a lot of that, I liked it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. Did you have a bicycle while you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Oh good gracious me no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 No. I know it wasn't the usual thing to get one 'till you worked and had saved up for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 No. I didn't have a bicycle ever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 You never had one. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 My sister had to have one because of when she went out to, when she first went out to work. It was only in the days of the tram then.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Well basketball at school I liked. But that was only once, oh, in a blue moon, you know, once every so often. But I liked basketball.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes. But there wasn't any other games or sports?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 No. Nothing that we went out to a field to play, no. Not like hockey or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Not even connected with your Welfare Club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Nothing in the way of outdoor games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Oh, we played tennis but I didn't excel in that at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Did you go to concerts or theatres, that sort of cultural thing; ballet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 
No. Again there was no one really that was interested not that I used to go with. And, I suppose, that normally I hadn't got pocket money to do it with. I did later or after I worked. We always used to go to the theatre, especially to the Gilbert and 
Sullivans. And I liked ballet too, but it was very rarely that I got anybody that liked it enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 And you had concerts though, at the club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 You used to perform in them yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 What parts did you play in those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Oh the lead sometimes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 The lead voice, you mean, in the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes, and... 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 There were plays were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes, we used to do full length plays. And the 'Enchanted Glen'. I was one of the leading speakers in that. We didn't have very mu
ch singing in that one. We had one from the junior choir which was more singing, that was 'The Lady of the Roses'. I had quite a good part in that. And the last one that I can remember that we did, it sounds awful, 'Princess JuJu and the Golden Amulet' - 
Princess JuJu! And another one, I can't remember the name of it for the life of me now, but I was the jester and everybody said it was the best part in the play.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 You enjoyed acting?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Oh yes. Very much. They put me on the stage when I was about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12919142\charrsid3743759 5}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759  years old in a little night shirt with a candle in my hand. There were about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11761595\charrsid3743759 12}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759  of the little children from the Sunday School. It was a Sunday School play, concert, you see; all the different classes taking part. And I was one of the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11761595\charrsid3743759  12 }
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 that had to say all sorts of things: "how would you like to... " and mine was "crawl up to the top of the stairs and find a great big ugly cat staring at you."
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 And did you remember your lines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 You did, yes. You've remembered it all that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Well that's one of those things you see again that ticks over.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Did you have trouble learning your parts for those plays, or did you find that quite easy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4616446 A  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Oh, I always found it very easy. I don't do so badly now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14642898 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 Cinemas, lantern slide shows, that kind of thing - was there anything like that you remember?
