I think as I told you the last time, that my father was a very keen card player. He used to love a game of cards. Cribbage and whist. Although he didn't like whist as much as he liked a game of crib. You could always get him to play a game of }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9726110\charrsid3743759 cricket}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4918359\charrsid3743759 , and some of the lesser games like Strip }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16018397\charrsid3743759 J}{\rtlch\fcs1 
